snippet.title: In My Shadow | Official Teaser
snippet.description:
In My Shadow takes you through a lamenting dream where you play with shadows in uniquely imaginative ways to solve twisted platforming puzzles.
Wishlist it on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1406200/In_My_Shadow/

Published by Alcon Interactive Group - https://www.alconent.com/aig/

Discord - https://discord.gg/UbQrumuwtr
Twitter - https://www.twitter.com/playbaegames
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/playbaegames
